<section class="ldh-section ldh-framework">
  <div class="ldh-section__heading">
    <span class="ldh-kicker">The Make it happen Framework</span>
    <h2>A clear path from intent to measurable value.</h2>
    <p>Move through six practical stages while applying five architecture lenses: Model, Build, Trust, Align and Lead.</p>
  </div>
  <ol class="ldh-framework__steps">
    <li><strong>Discover</strong><span>Align business needs, value, constraints and stakeholders.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Design</strong><span>Model the target state, flows, decisions and architecture principles.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Build</strong><span>Implement the platform, integrations and cloud components.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Trust</strong><span>Embed governance, quality, security, metadata and ownership.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Deliver</strong><span>Lead execution, dependencies, adoption and go-live.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Scale</strong><span>Standardize, measure impact and continuously improve.</span></li>
  </ol>
</section>
